text: Miesinnei Mercy Genesis (born 20 September 1997) is a Nigerian freestyle wrestler. At the 2016 Summer Olympics she competed in the Women’s freestyle -48 kg. In 2020, she won the gold medal in the women's freestyle 50 kg event at the 2020 African Wrestling Championships. ==References== Category:Olympic wrestlers of Nigeria Category:1997 births Category:Wrestlers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Living people Category:African Games gold medalists for Nigeria Category:African Games medalists in wrestling Category:Competitors at the 2015 African Games Category:Competitors at the 2019 African Games Category:African Games competitors for Nigeria
